lyrics:
[Intro]
Yo, yo, yo, Sfera in the house
Bringing the flavor of the streets, no doubt
Pizza and spaghetti, can never get enough
Turn up the beat, let it scorch

[Verse 1]
In the streets of Naples, under the blazing sun
Rolling with my crew, sensing the burning fun
Pizza in hand, mozzarella so divine
Flavor exploding, like a majestic vine

Classical Margherita or maybe a Diavola
Spicy taste leading me to reach diploma
From narrow alleys to the grand square
Rap meets pizza, a profound affair
